window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Surviving Lord Darius' attack has put Elorion's level over the top. He must soon leave the Mistress' Labyrinth for the unknown dangers of the Underworld.</p> <p>There are three paths that stand before him. Should he absorb all the Blue Magic he can find, power level his fellow captives, or take on the bone palace alone?</p> <p>The Underworld is waiting....</p>"; 
